dct_title_s: Map of part of Yemen (from Niebuhr) to accompany the paper by Dr. C. Millingen
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Major mountains, wadis, and settlements are shown. 15°N parallel is shown. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 44 (1874), pp. 118-26; held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v. 44 1874
